snippet.title: SilvaGunner Rebooted (Full Playthrough)
snippet.description:
Part of the new SiIvaGunner ARG. You can currently grab the link here: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1eJpnC5Ft6iGgzMj7admnKMiCr2Z1Uu1M2xaaRKjCQCQ/edit?tab=t.0
EDIT: the game has now been officially linked on the channel, listed here: https://youtu.be/8yPtESJYQ-g

Also check out Moder112's playthrough here, who managed to upload it before me: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZRsYyZhF_2w
